           hits the remaining edge of the slit. See the session.autoRaiseDelay resource for the delay time.
 
       Auto raise        Автоматический подъем
           If this is enabled the slit will elevate after a defined time when the mouse pointer enters the it. It will fall back when the cursor
           leaves the slit. See the session.autoRaiseDelay resource for the delay time.

       Maximize Over     Максимизировать Над выше
           Enabling this option will allow windows to maximizing over the slit. With this switched off they will only expand to the edge of the
           slit. This option may be overridden by the “Full Maximization” from the Configuration Menu. If that option is enabled, this option will
